name: Space Jump
description:
Hello guys!! This is my first game which I made in unity 3D and i wish you like it. Looking forward to receive feedback from you. It will help me grow.

A bit about the game..... You are this crazy guy who got stuck in space with this skull head who has a bad sense of humor and does not like you. Your object is to jump and notch up your best time and try and survive for longer!!!

BOTTOM LINE.... I am this crazy guys who loves to make and play games and dreams big.....
